Package: g15stats
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: LCD system stats monitor for Logitech G15 displays
 G15Stats displays live system information on Logitech G15 LCD devices.
 It provides screens for CPU load, memory, swap, network traffic,
 temperatures, fan speeds, battery state, and CPU frequency.
 .
 Configuration is supported via YAML files and command-line options.
 A user systemd service unit is provided for per-user operation.
